OL,5,G1800 This is BBC Scotland
OL,6,G1900 Reporting Scotland: News at Seven
OL,7,G1915 Gold Town
OL,8,     F3/3. Documentary following the
OL,9,     Ffortunes of a band of gold miners.
OL,10,     FThis episode sees the pandemic
OL,11,     Fhitting the UK, causing all mining
OL,12,     Fto stop and local businesses to
OL,13,     Ftake a huge hit.
OL,14,G2015 The Repair Shop on the Road
OL,15,     FThe team help commemorate the
OL,16,     Fvictims of the Lockerbie bombing,
OL,17,     Fautomata expert Michael tackles a
OL,18,     Fclockwork train, and Kirsten gets
OL,19,     Fhands-on with medieval slipware
OL,20,     Fpottery.
